    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "In NIEPMD , first of all you are fascinated by the surrounding. It is a institution situated in ECR road and just beside u can see the Bay of bengal sea,beach is there. While you are having a class u can feel the natural breeze and colour of blue sea",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "Secondly, The cleanliness and management is too good. It is the best of all. Big hall for functions, examinations ,library, ac rooms, mess.",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "As it is multiple disability institute. So you get every intervention in a same roof.People can avail services like Physiotherapy, Occupation therapy, Speech Therapy, Psychology, Special school for specially abled. So no need to wander her and there.",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "Here the Teacher and Professor are highly professional and helpful. They clear the doubts in one to one interaction. Proper demonstration of exercise and modalities are shown to us. Then we apply to the patients",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "As it is national institute , u can interact with other states people too, you can learn new languages , culture and traditions",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "Clinical exposure will be much better than other colleges",
          "name": "Gavesh Vaishnav",
          "course_tag_name": "BOT"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Here actually student strength is low in batch.",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "New innovation for teaching can be improved here.",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "Mess food here needs to be changed and sports activites should be increased",
          "name": "Amiya Ballav ROY",
          "course_tag_name": "B.P.T"
        },
        {
          "text": "No hostel facilities for students after first year",
          "name": "Gavesh Vaishnav",
          "course_tag_name": "BOT"
        },
        {
          "text": "No bus facilities for students for day scholars and outside first year  hostellers",
          "name": "Gavesh Vaishnav",
          "course_tag_name": "BOT"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen food is not good as per students need",
          "name": "Gavesh Vaishnav",
